text: Agua Blanca (Spanish: "White Water") may refer to several geographical locations: ==In Mexico== *Agua Blanca, Coahuila *Agua Blanca de Iturbide, Hidalgo *Agua Blanca, Oaxaca *Agua Blanca, Sonora ==Other places== *Agua Blanca (La Rioja), Argentina *Agua Blanca, Ecuador *Agua Blanca, Jutiapa, Guatemala *Agua Blanca District, El Dorado Province, San Martín Region, Peru *Agua Blanca (Ibiza), Spain *Agua Blanca, Portuguesa, municipality in Venezuela ==See also== *Whitewater (disambiguation)
title: Agua Blanca
